### Generate Tracking Link
POST http://localhost:3000/tracking/links
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destinationUrl": "https://genfeed.ai/pricing",
  "contentId": "{{testVideoId}}",
  "contentType": "video",
  "platform": "instagram",
  "campaignName": "Product Launch",
  "utm": {
    "source": "instagram",
    "medium": "social",
    "campaign": "product_launch"
  }
}

### Get Tracking Link Stats
GET http://localhost:3000/tracking/links/{{testLinkId}}/stats

### Get All Tracking Links
GET http://localhost:3000/tracking/links?page=1&limit=20

### Track Click
POST http://localhost:3000/tracking/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "linkId": "{{testLinkId}}",
  "userAgent": "Mozilla/5.0...",
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.1",
  "referrer": "https://instagram.com"
}

### Get Link Clicks
GET http://localhost:3000/tracking/links/{{testLinkId}}/clicks?page=1&limit=20

### Delete Tracking Link
DELETE http://localhost:3000/tracking/links/{{testLinkId}}

